- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used for 3 core patterns with correct `#if NET7_0_OR_GREATER` guard
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ `.All()`
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` and `WordCount` use efficient char-by-char iteration
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `ToLowerInvariant()` correctly

